abstract: Rances Bathelemy beats Antonio DeMarco by unanimous decision in junior welterweight bout to stay undefeated.
lead_paragraph: Rances Barthelemy beat the former lightweight titleholder Antonio DeMarco by unanimous decision in a junior welterweight bout in Las Vegas.
